    <lb n="12"/>κ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">αὶ</unclear> ων ὧν δέ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">δ</unclear>ωκεν Κρίτωνι. 

    <lb n="13"/><expan><ex cert="high">ἔτους</ex></expan> <num value="29">κθ</num> Δαισίου <num value="23">κγ</num>. ἐν Ἀρσινόηι. 

